<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   CNN to Receive
   $3.5 Million Grant
   From Foundation
   ---
   Funds Will Be Used to Defray
   Network's Coverage Costs
   Of Presidential Campaign
   ----
   By Kevin Goldman
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
10/14/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
</SO>
<CO>
   GE TBSA TBSB
</CO>
